						               													<description>New Card Game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Transparent and waterproof SHOOTHIT Playing Cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;compound:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Complete set of 54 cards: 52 playing cards and 2 rule cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game based on 4 different suits of 13 cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;(Suits: Circle, Triangle, Penta, Square)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;HOW PLAY&amp;#10;&amp;#10;THE GAME&amp;#10;The game is very simple, if you know how to count you know how to play, you just have to add one.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After dealing all the cards that we cannot seen, each player reveals on his turn a card from his covered deck to his right. Witch he will try to mount to the central deck or mount on the other player or himself, if not, he leave the card on his right.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Creating like this on the right the undercover deck.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ex: the 5 over the 4 (mounting in an always increasing way)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When a player draws an Ace, he leave the card on the center, creates the center deck and distributes a penalty to all players.Only in the central deck the numbers and ALSO the SUIT hve to be respected.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When the player place a card he have the right to reveal the next one.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;ONLY 1 RULE: SHOOTHIT have only a important rule, and it's, you have to try to mount the cards already revealed  to your right before revealing another one.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;And now you know how play SHOOTHIT!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The rules don't change but only the penalties according to the game mode.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
